decl: example : s ∪ f ⁻¹' u ⊆ f ⁻¹' (f '' s ∪ u)
og_raw:
example : s ∪ f ⁻¹' u ⊆ f ⁻¹' (f '' s ∪ u) := by
  rintro x (xs | fxu)
  · left
    exact ⟨x, xs, rfl⟩
  right; exact fxu
new_raw:
example : s ∪ f ⁻¹' u ⊆ f ⁻¹' (f '' s ∪ u)  := by
  rintro x (xs | fxu)
  exact Or.inl ⟨x, xs, rfl⟩
  exact Or.inr fxu

decl: example : (f '' ⋃ i, A i) = ⋃ i, f '' A i
og_raw:
example : (f '' ⋃ i, A i) = ⋃ i, f '' A i := by
  ext y; simp
  constructor
  · rintro ⟨x, ⟨i, xAi⟩, fxeq⟩
    use i, x
  rintro ⟨i, x, xAi, fxeq⟩
  exact ⟨x, ⟨i, xAi⟩, fxeq⟩
new_raw:

  · rintro ⟨x, ⟨i, xAi⟩, fxeq⟩
    use i, x

  exact ⟨x, ⟨i, xAi⟩, fxeq⟩

decl: example : (f '' ⋂ i, A i) ⊆ ⋂ i, f '' A i
og_raw:
example : (f '' ⋂ i, A i) ⊆ ⋂ i, f '' A i := by
  intro y; simp
  intro x h fxeq i
  use x
  exact ⟨h i, fxeq⟩
